{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/blank0.png?t=1733869663\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Being a piece of bread, you naturally crave a stack of pancakes for breakfast. To start off your day and, more importantly, fill your stomach, you set off on a journey to get the best pancakes in town. However, you soon realize you have no clue where the bakery is. Thankfully, it seems like an intruder in your house may just know where you can find it...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/jump.gif?t=1733869663\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this casual platformer, you  explore environments ranging from your home to space. Though getting to your end goal doesn't seem   hard at first, you soon find that the path there is a tad convoluted, with enemy desserts jumping around at every turn, trying to stop you. Not to mention, your new friend seems to enjoy messing around with you a bit.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/extras/Dialogue.gif?t=1733869663\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you're looking for a low-stress way to take a break, this may just be the game for you. :)</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733869663","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/page.bg.jpg?t=1733869663","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208250/320a045a38ce57037b940e883aab3c81a672da7a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733869663","capsule_imagev5